9Ô∏è‚É£ Dashboard Design Story

Executive clarity: KPIs at the top, filters on the left.

Expandable sections let users focus on individual or portfolio analysis.

Charts highlight risk distribution and model transparency.

Export buttons ensure data is ready for reporting or presentations.

üîü Getting Started

Clone the repo and install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt


Run the Streamlit app:

streamlit run app.py


Use the sidebar to select mode and download the CSV template if needed.

Explore KPIs, filters, individual assessment, and simulations.

Export reports as needed.

‚úÖ Key Notes

Check uploaded CSV for column consistency.

Use realistic values for single customer assessment for accurate AI verdicts.

KPI values and charts dynamically reflect selected filters.

Model: Random Forest classifier with engineered features for actionable insights.